.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-19::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg       |
| Hobby      | traveling     | skydiving  |
| Pet        | goat          | chinchilla |

