.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, roller
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | romance |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | bolivar  |
| Transport     | roller | boat    |

 